import React from "react";
import Accordion from "@mui/material/Accordion";
import AccordionSummary from "@mui/material/AccordionSummary";
import AccordionDetails from "@mui/material/AccordionDetails";
import Typography from "@mui/material/Typography";
import ExpandMoreIcon from "@mui/icons-material/ExpandMore";
import {  DiscountOutlined } from "@mui/icons-material";
import {
  AddressCheckout,
  AddressDiv,
  AvailableofferDiv,
  AvaOffer,
  BagCheckout,
  CartItems,
  CartLeft,
  CartRight,
  ChangeButton,
  Container,
  DeliverTo,
  DotsCheckout,
  FirstOffer,
  Logo,
  NavCheckOutSteps,
  NavContainer,
  NavLogo,
  NavSecure,
  PaymentCheckout,
  SecureLogo,
  SecureN,
  TopLA,
} from "./Cart.element";

const Cart = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <NavContainer>
        <NavLogo>
          <Logo src="https://images.indianexpress.com/2021/01/myntra.png" />
        </NavLogo>
        <NavCheckOutSteps>
          <BagCheckout>BAG</BagCheckout>
          <DotsCheckout>---------</DotsCheckout>
          <AddressCheckout>ADDRESS</AddressCheckout>
          <DotsCheckout>---------</DotsCheckout>
          <PaymentCheckout>PAYMENT</PaymentCheckout>
        </NavCheckOutSteps>
        <NavSecure>
          <SecureLogo src="https://constant.myntassets.com/checkout/assets/img/sprite-secure.png" />
          <SecureN>100% SECURE</SecureN>
        </NavSecure>
      </NavContainer>
      <CartItems>
        <CartLeft>
          <AddressDiv>
            <DeliverTo>Deliver To:</DeliverTo>
            <ChangeButton>CHANGE ADDRESS</ChangeButton>
          </AddressDiv>

          <AvailableofferDiv>
            <TopLA>
              <DiscountOutlined sx={{ width: "20px", height: "20px" }} />
              <AvaOffer>Available Offers</AvaOffer>
            </TopLA>
            <FirstOffer>
              10% Instant Discount on American Express Cards on a min spend of
              Rs 3,500. TCA
            </FirstOffer>
            <Accordion>
              <AccordionSummary
                expandIcon={
                  <ExpandMoreIcon
                    sx={{
                      color: "#ff3f6c",
                      marginLeft: "-530px",
                      fontSize: "12px",
                    }}
                  />
                }
                aria-controls="panel1a-content"
                id="panel1a-header"
              >
                <Typography sx={{ color: "#ff3f6c", fontSize: "12px" }}>
                  Show More
                </Typography>
              </AccordionSummary>
              <AccordionDetails>
                <Typography sx={{ fontSize: "12px" }}>
                  10% Instant Discount on Bank Of Baroda Credit cards on a min
                  spend of Rs 3,000.TCA
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ fontSize: "12px" }}>
                  5% Unlimited Cashback on Flipkart Axis Bank Credit Card. TCA
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ fontSize: "12px" }}>
                  10% Cashback upto Rs 100 on Paytm Postpaid transaction on a
                  min spend of Rs 1000 . TCA
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ fontSize: "12px" }}>
                  15% Cashback upto Rs 150 on Freecharge Paylater transaction.
                  TCA
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ fontSize: "12px" }}>
                  10% Cashback upto Rs 200 on Ola Money Postpaid or wallet
                  transaction on a min spend of Rs 1000 . TCA
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ fontSize: "12px" }}>
                  Upto Rs 500 Cashback on Mobikwik Wallet Transactions on a min
                  spend of Rs 999.Use code MBK500 on Mobikwik. TCA{" "}
                </Typography>
              </AccordionDetails>
            </Accordion>
          </AvailableofferDiv>
        </CartLeft>
        <CartRight></CartRight>
      </CartItems>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Cart;
